  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This data base has been set in order to gather oncogeriatric information from elderly
      patients with pancreatic cancer who underwent an oncogeriatric evaluation.

      ONCOGEPAN database gathers data from deux institutions (Institut Paoli-Calmettes and
      Assistance Publique des Hôpitaux de Marseille) involved in Marseille SIRIC (Integrated Cancer
      Research Site).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
